items.title: Home Depot’s (HD) $5.5B GMS Acquisition Solidifies Bullish Analyst Confidence
items.description: The Home Depot, Inc. (NYSE:HD) is one of the top e-commerce stocks with long-term potential. On July 1, DA Davidson reaffirmed its Buy rating and $450 price target for Home Depot (NYSE:HD) after the company finalized a deal to acquire GMS for $110 per share, totaling a $5.5 billion enterprise value.
